de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.web

Interface Uploader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TeLiProUploader, WebHrsUploader

    public interface Uploader
    If there are plans to support additional webinterface in the sensorplatform in the future, this interface may become useful. Username, password, cookies and all other data should be stored in the class which implements this interface. Since there is only one webinterface with a fixed, predefined workflow, this interface may need to be changed to properly fit for connection to different webinterfaces. Implementations of this interface will be bound by Guice to the Uploader interface, dependent on the project setup. An Uploader is intended to be used as Singleton, enforced by Guice.
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka
